{"tid":1425140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"揾人答我，不合作運動嘅目的係乜","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:16:01.000Z","uid":215341,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"53aaab8ab95cef3573ac6e00a4685730e63e1f08","tid":1425140,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"講真，放火打狗圍狗屋整核彈，我都唔撚割，有目的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但我想問，港鐵個不合作運動有乜撚野用？</span><br />\n<br />\n對佢公司冇影響，對政府冇影響，對班狗都冇影響，唯一影響嘅得市民，藍嘅更藍，淺黃同中立隨時變立場，做嚟做乜柒？<br />\n我黃撚都閪咁都質礙個港鐵不合作成效，冇市民撐，得巴絲自己圍爐有用咩？"},{"pid":"e84b7e29b2b2cabcb65ddb1586b1f3c48bbbbd5f","tid":1425140,"uid":27718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/04/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%94%BF%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%9D%EF%BC%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA/?fbclid=IwAR39SastuJ7wayZi2sRU0sRTZAYKeCPs9LiZkbdEWxwgfu7J1aQFNIsM_xY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorrupttheyouth.net%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25A1%259D%25EF%25BC%259F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR39SastuJ7wayZi2sRU0sRTZAYKeCPs9LiZkbdEWxwgfu7J1aQFNIsM_xY&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=6fa7d777\" target=\"_blank\">https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/04/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%94%BF%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%9D%EF%BC%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA/?fbclid=IwAR39SastuJ7wayZi2sRU0sRTZAYKeCPs9LiZkbdEWxwgfu7J1aQFNIsM_xY</a><br />\n一直以來，不民主政府的最大問題是它沒有聽取民意的需要，而這些不合作運動就是要增加抗爭者的籌碼，讓政府有需要讓步。誠然，只是短暫堵塞一兩條地鐵線，或一兩天的巴士慢駛引致道路擠塞，不會造成多大的影響。但正如勇武抗爭初時會給警察輕易清場一樣，這些不合作運動也要有個升級的過程。當過程慢慢提升，由塞一兩條線變成塞六七條線，由慢駛一兩日變成常態慢駛，不滿的不只市民，還包括大商家，這樣的話，政府的壓力就會大增，最終有了討論與讓步的需要。<br />\n<br />\n  當然，這過程當中一定會有無辜市民受影響。但我們可以問，有哪一種抗爭手法，沒有人會受影響？可能阻礙地鐵開出真的侵害到你的權利，但比較勇武抗爭抗爭者所受的傷和犠牲，比起通過法例後受壓迫的人民要付出的代價，遲到上班的傷害實在是小太多。有可能這是必要之惡，是社會進步必需要付出的小代價。"},{"pid":"6dc9376fdd1c97d0a832416b9dd48139c4af95ab","tid":1425140,"uid":27718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"簡單D黎講係畀壓力你同你腦細，等你同你腦細都一齊叫政府快啲搞掂佢舊屎"},{"pid":"faeb929a6e9bf8b79855fcbd012a5a599fc51ddb","tid":1425140,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e84b7e29b2b2cabcb65ddb1586b1f3c48bbbbd5f","tid":1425140,"uid":27718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/04/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%94%BF%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%9D%EF%BC%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA/?fbclid=IwAR39SastuJ7wayZi2sRU0sRTZAYKeCPs9LiZkbdEWxwgfu7J1aQFNIsM_xY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorrupttheyouth.net%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25A1%259D%25EF%25BC%259F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR39SastuJ7wayZi2sRU0sRTZAYKeCPs9LiZkbdEWxwgfu7J1aQFNIsM_xY&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=6fa7d777\" target=\"_blank\">https://corrupttheyouth.net/2019/08/04/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%94%BF%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%9D%EF%BC%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA/?fbclid=IwAR39SastuJ7wayZ